                    <button type="button" onclick="closeUserModal()" class="flex-1 bg-gray-300 text-gray-700 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-400 transition duration-200">‡∏¢‡∏Å‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¥‡∏Å</button>
